{
  "stem": "9.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As a child, I was taught that Poland is the greatest and the best, most wonderful country in the world.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Later I found out, when Hitler invaded Poland, we had one airplane, which was taken apart for cleaning, and we didn't have any aviation whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Polish army on horses was fighting the German army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, obviously, Poland was taken over in something-- was 10 days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Germans came to about center of Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then suddenly the Russians started coming from the east.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "At that point, my parents hired a wagon with horses, because that's all there was available.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we decided to run to Romanian border.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When we were on the border already, we heard the Russians are coming.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Well, my parents made a very unwise decision.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I hope nobody makes these kind of decisions again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They decided to go back to save few more pillows.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The possessions were important to them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Instead of running and getting out, because through Romania we could get out and come to United States at that time or to South America, they decided to go back, and that was the end of it.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They never came out alive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Immediately the Russians [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] started-- took away our business, naturally.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in our apartment, the fellow whom we fed from a very poor family [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] decided that he's a Communist, and we're the capitalists.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he came to our apartment, insisted that my mother brings the food to him while he's laying in bed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was-- had the satisfaction of making a mother-- a slave out of her.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we fed him and his family for many, many years, but he felt he's s Communist.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
